    <item>
      <title>2024 年俄罗斯预算石油收入将激增近三分之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/russia-s-budget-oil-revenue-spiked-by-almost-a-third-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着俄罗斯适应国际制裁，原油价格上涨，推动该国国家预算的石油收入去年增长近三分之一，达到至少 2018 年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/russia-s-budget-oil-revenue-spiked-by-almost-a-third-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:57:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维克库宁称波罗的海电缆被切断“绝非偶然”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/virkkunen-cut-cables-in-baltic-can-t-be-by-accident-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟新任数字事务负责人 Henna Virkkunen 表示，波罗的海电缆多次断裂事件“如果每年发生多次，那么这肯定不是偶然事件”。她在接受彭博社 Oliver Crook 采访时这样说道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/virkkunen-cut-cables-in-baltic-can-t-be-by-accident-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sage Therapeutics 接受 Biogen 4.69 亿美元的报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sage-therapeutics-jumps-on-biogen-s-469-million-takeover-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Biogen Inc. 提出以约 4.69 亿美元收购这家专注于神经科学的制药商后，Sage Therapeutics Inc. 的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sage-therapeutics-jumps-on-biogen-s-469-million-takeover-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lululemon 因节日销售强劲而重获增长动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/lululemon-regains-momentum-on-strong-holiday-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lululemon Athletica Inc. 预计第四季度销售额将超过市场预期，这表明该高端运动服品牌正在抵御新兴竞争对手和消费者支出增长放缓的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/lululemon-regains-momentum-on-strong-holiday-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布后，美国国债抛售引发全球市场恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/treasuries-selloff-ripples-through-world-markets-after-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五公布的强劲就业报告增强了人们对美联储将在今年几乎全年暂停降息的猜测，美国国债延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/treasuries-selloff-ripples-through-world-markets-after-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国对俄罗斯的制裁威胁供应，油价创下五个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，威胁到全球最大产油国之一的石油供应，油价上涨至五个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息希望渺茫，科技股受创：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储重新调整利率预测后，交易员们正在等待关键的通胀数据，股市最具影响力的集团的抛售加剧了华尔街的焦虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 22:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
